users.functions.profile_1: Allows to display the parameters configured in all applications without any additional functionality. Back-up and History screens are excluded.
users.functions.profile_2: Allows to perform, from the supervision application, remote commands on the units from the supervision application: RESET, BITE, Main Switching/RCS of radio units, RF Test (loop mode), Access to MIB-2 of each CPU, Activation/Deactivation of services.(Must have assigned at least the display profile).
users.profile_3: Inhibition of historical alarms in GW (RCS)
users.functions.profile_3: Allows configuring that the events generated by certain gateways, generate alarm states or not, in the system (at least the visualization profile must be assigned)
users.functions.profile_4: Allows to acknowledge alarms from the RCS monitoring application.
users.functions.profile_5: Allows to perform all functions related to the assignment of profiles/roles to users for all applications (CFIGR+RCS+CFIGL), from the user menu of the CFIGR application.
users.functions.profile_6: Allows to set which database configurations are to be monitored or not.
users.functions.profile_7: Full control of all applications and devices.
users.functions.profile_8: Allows to visualize the parameters configured in the local configuration application of the gateways.
users.functions.profile_9: Full control of the gateways local configuration application
users.functions.profile_10: Allows access and management of the CFIGR and RCS application history service, from the CFIGR application's history_maintenance menu.
users.functions.profile_11: Allows to configure the automatic BACKUP system of the system.
users.functions.profile_12: Allows to enable / disable the acoustic level of alarm signaling.
users.functions.profile_13: Allows to perform the following functions from the gateways: Management of local preconfigurations (import, export, save, upload and delete), Modification of parameters and apply the changes.
users.functions.profile_14: Allows to load new software versions in the gateways.
users.functions.profile_15: Allows the design of configurations in the CFIGR application and their loading / activation.
